      "Florida Section 404 assumption was in legal dispute at time of publication",
      "Asterisked entries have qualifications explained in state-by-state analysis \u2014 simplified to true/false here with notes"
    ],
    "notes": "FAI is the Foundation for American Innovation, a policy think tank. Per Ultan sourcing standards, this is tier-4 (advocacy). However, the underlying data references primary government sources (state regulations, EPA approvals, SIPs) which are tier-1. The checklists are structured factual assessments, not advocacy claims. Part 1: Samuel Roland, June 2024. Part 2: Samuel Roland, November 2025."
